Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.53,0:35:14.55,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Forgive us please, we’ve come so far
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.93,0:35:17.62,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,There’s nowhere else to go
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.25,0:35:24.30,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But if you~ are his Queen, then
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.60,0:35:29.10,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You~ should know~ the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.94,0:35:33.34,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All the gems and the coal
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.60,0:35:36.19,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Every mare and every foal
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.41,0:35:40.99,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Toil on under the weight~ of their shackles!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.55,0:35:44.14,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We once lived so proud and~ free!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.32,0:35:46.88,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Now the dark and vicious king
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.03,0:35:51.30,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Has their minds captured in shadow and enslaved!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.56,0:35:52.35,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,So we come
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.89,0:35:55.88,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To call on you
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.21,0:35:56.93,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Only then
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.50,0:36:00.60,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Will they make it through
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.90,0:36:01.54,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Save~ us!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.19,0:36:05.44,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For only you can
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.59,0:36:06.15,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Save~ us!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.25,0:36:12.53,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,From the shadow king
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.59,0:36:40.57,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Luna, what say you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.88,0:36:42.86,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It’s your path to choose
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.61,0:36:47.44,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Knowing what we might have to do
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.96,0:36:49.84,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We cannot delay
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.25,0:36:52.24,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Though I feel dismay
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.95,0:36:56.85,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We both know there’s no other way
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.29,0:37:22.39,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Forgive me please
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.91,0:37:25.39,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,He's gone too far
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.54,0:37:29.06,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I tru~ly didn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.94,0:37:33.07,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Above all else
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.56,0:37:40.72,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,My duty lies with all~ of you~
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.59,0:37:44.03,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Then it’s time to prepare
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.32,0:37:46.80,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,By the snow and by the~ air
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.06,0:37:51.68,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We must march upon the gates~ of his empire
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.24,0:37:54.45,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,With the magic we face
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.79,0:37:57.56,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A wicked evil he’s embraced
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.75,0:38:01.84,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We must fight to set the crystal ponies free!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.25,0:38:02.96,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,So we go
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.57,0:38:06.56,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To heed the call
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.90,0:38:07.57,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Knowing we
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.26,0:38:11.06,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Must free them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.55,0:38:12.26,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Save~ them!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.88,0:38:16.09,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For he must fall, to
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.24,0:38:16.95,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Save~ them!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.86,0:38:23.03,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,From what he’s be~come